Eligibility and Applications
Summary of eligibility and applications received:
Eligible Library Systems Eligible 14 Library Systems applying 12 Purchase Option Grant systems 37 Purchase Option Grant systems applying 12 Number of these applied to appeal their eligibility 7
While the state library agency is not required to submit an application, they have requested the Gates Library Computer grant for which they are eligible.
Eligible library buildings not applying: * Providence Athenaeum * Redwood Library and Athenaeum
Supplemental Training Lab grant has been approved for: * Providence Public Library
Appeals
There were a total of 9 appeals.
1 appeal has been approved.
Libraries appealing eligibility status or appealing for more computers than for which they were originally eligible:
Library Appealing for: Approval East Providence Public Library Eligibility for cash grant Yes West Warwick Public Library System 6 PCs - originally eligible for 4 No Barrington Public Library Eligibility for cash grant No Exeter Public Library Eligibility for cash grant No Island Free Library Eligibility for cash grant No Lincoln Public Library Eligibility for cash grant No Marion J. Mohr Memorial Library Eligibility for cash grant No Tiverton Library Services Eligibility for cash grant No Westerly Public Library Eligibility for cash grant No
