Additional Spanish Keyboard Requests
2 library buildings requested Spanish keyboards in addition to the number for which they are eligible, for a total of 5 additional Spanish keyboards.
System Library Building # of add'l Spanish keyboards Central Falls Free Public Library Central Falls Free Public Library 1 Pawtucket Public Library Pawtucket Public Library 4
Also, the library approved for the Supplemental Training Lab grant, Providence Public Library, has requested Spanish keyboards for all 11 of their computers.
Next Event
Before Your Computer Arrives (BYCA) Workshops February 19, 2003 (tentative)
Several of these will be held at various locations around RI. Eligible Library Building Grant recipients are required to attend this workshop, which provides information on planning and preparing the library for your computers.
Library buildings that are eligible for Purchase Option Grants and are considering buying Gates Library Computers are also required to attend this workshop, as ordering information will be distributed at this time.
More information to follow from the Gates Foundation.
Other dates are posted on the Timeline.
